{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Cilium Agent Pod Status",
      "description": "Shows the status of Cilium agent pods across all nodes. Panels shows running vs non-running pods.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Pods",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Running"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "green",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Not Running"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "red",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_pod_status_phase{pod=~\"cilium-.*\", namespace=\"kube-system\", phase=\"Running\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Running",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "count(kube_pod_status_phase{pod=~\"cilium-.*\", namespace=\"kube-system\", phase!=\"Running\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "Not Running",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Cilium Endpoint Count",
      "description": "Tracks the number of Cilium-managed endpoints by state. A healthy cluster should show most endpoints in 'ready' state.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Endpoints",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (state) (cilium_endpoint_state)",
          "legendFormat": "{{state}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Policy Drops (Hubble)",
      "description": "Tracks packet drops reported by Hubble, grouped by drop reason. Spikes after migration may indicate missing policy rules.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Drops/sec",
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (reason) (rate(hubble_drop_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "DNS Query Latency (Hubble)",
      "description": "DNS response time distribution observed by Hubble. High latencies after migration may indicate DNS policy issues.",
      "type": "heatmap",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "scheme",
            "schemeId": "Oranges"
          },
          "custom": {
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            }
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "calculate": true,
        "calculation": {
          "xBuckets": {
            "mode": "size"
          },
          "yBuckets": {
            "mode": "size",
            "scale": {
              "log": 2,
              "type": "log"
            }
          }
        },
        "cellGap": 1,
        "color": {
          "exponent": 0.5,
          "fill": "dark-orange",
          "mode": "scheme",
          "scale": "exponential",
          "schemeId": "Oranges",
          "steps": 64
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "show": true,
          "yHistogram": true
        },
        "yAxis": {
          "axisLabel": "Latency",
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(hubble_dns_response_time_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)",
          "legendFormat": "{{le}}",
          "format": "heatmap",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "TCP Connection Status (Hubble)",
      "description": "TCP flag distribution observed by Hubble. Shows SYN, SYN-ACK, FIN, and RST rates to track connection health.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Packets/sec",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "pps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "RST"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "red",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "SYN"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "blue",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (flag) (rate(hubble_tcp_flags_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{flag}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Node Reimage Progress",
      "description": "Tracks the number of nodes in Ready condition versus total nodes. During migration, nodes are reimaged to switch from NPM to Cilium.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 16
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Nodes",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Nodes Ready"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "green",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Total Nodes"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "blue",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_node_status_condition{condition=\"Ready\", status=\"true\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Nodes Ready",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "count(kube_node_status_condition{condition=\"Ready\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Total Nodes",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Migration Checklist",
      "description": "Step-by-step checklist for NPM-to-Cilium migration.",
      "type": "text",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## NPM-to-Cilium Migration Checklist\n\n### Pre-Migration\n- [ ] Run `npm-audit` to identify breaking policy changes\n- [ ] Resolve all FAIL findings from the audit report\n- [ ] Run `npm-conntest snapshot --phase pre-migration` to capture baseline connectivity\n- [ ] Run `npm-migrate --dry-run` to preview the migration plan\n- [ ] Review generated policy patches in the output directory\n- [ ] Verify no Windows node pools exist (Cilium does not support Windows)\n\n### Migration Execution\n- [ ] Run `npm-migrate` to execute the full migration\n- [ ] Monitor Cilium agent pod status (panel above) \u2014 all agents should reach Running\n- [ ] Monitor endpoint count (panel above) \u2014 should match pre-migration pod count\n- [ ] Watch for policy drops (panel above) \u2014 new drops indicate missing rules\n- [ ] Verify DNS latency remains stable (panel above)\n- [ ] Confirm all nodes reimage successfully (panel above)\n\n### Post-Migration\n- [ ] Run `npm-conntest validate --pre-snapshot <path>` to verify no regressions\n- [ ] Review any new connectivity changes (NewAllows) for security implications\n- [ ] Verify LoadBalancer and NodePort services are reachable\n- [ ] Confirm kube-proxy removal did not break service mesh (Istio/Linkerd)\n- [ ] Update monitoring dashboards to use Cilium/Hubble metrics\n- [ ] Remove old NPM-related resources and configurations\n- [ ] Document any CiliumNetworkPolicies added during migration"
      }
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": [
    "npm",
    "cilium",
    "migration",
    "kubernetes",
    "aks"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {
          "selected": false,
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "Prometheus"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Datasource",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "NPM to Cilium Migration Monitor",
  "uid": "npm-cilium-migration-monitor",
  "version": 1
}
